ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of GLENN S. SAKAKI of Oakville, Ontario, to be Vice-Chairperson of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Nicholas Offord, whose term has expired.
